```python
def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace(" ", "H ")

print(insert_before_character("Hello world")) # "HelloH world"
print(insert_before_character("Hello big  world")) # "HelloH bigH  world"
print(insert_before_character("Hello")) # "Hello"
print(insert_before_character("")) # ""
```
